[
  {
    "id": 4902,
    "number": 1,
    "key": "55:1",
    "textAr": "ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنُ",
    "textEn": "The Most Merciful",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4903,
    "number": 2,
    "key": "55:2",
    "textAr": "عَلَّمَ ٱلْقُرْءَانَ",
    "textEn": "Taught the Qur’ān,",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4904,
    "number": 3,
    "key": "55:3",
    "textAr": "خَلَقَ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ",
    "textEn": "Created man,",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4905,
    "number": 4,
    "key": "55:4",
    "textAr": "عَلَّمَهُ ٱلْبَيَانَ",
    "textEn": "[And] taught him eloquence.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4906,
    "number": 5,
    "key": "55:5",
    "textAr": "ٱلشَّمْسُ وَٱلْقَمَرُ بِحُسْبَانٍ",
    "textEn": "The sun and the moon [move] by precise calculation,",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4907,
    "number": 6,
    "key": "55:6",
    "textAr": "وَٱلنَّجْمُ وَٱلشَّجَرُ يَسْجُدَانِ",
    "textEn": "And the stars and trees prostrate.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4908,
    "number": 7,
    "key": "55:7",
    "textAr": "وَٱلسَّمَآءَ رَفَعَهَا وَوَضَعَ ٱلْمِيزَانَ",
    "textEn": "And the heaven He raised and imposed the balance",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4909,
    "number": 8,
    "key": "55:8",
    "textAr": "أَلَّا تَطْغَوْا۟ فِى ٱلْمِيزَانِ",
    "textEn": "That you not transgress within the balance.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4910,
    "number": 9,
    "key": "55:9",
    "textAr": "وَأَقِيمُوا۟ ٱلْوَزْنَ بِٱلْقِسْطِ وَلَا تُخْسِرُوا۟ ٱلْمِيزَانَ",
    "textEn": "And establish weight in justice and do not make deficient the balance.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4911,
    "number": 10,
    "key": "55:10",
    "textAr": "وَٱلْأَرْضَ وَضَعَهَا لِلْأَنَامِ",
    "textEn": "And the earth He laid [out] for the creatures.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4912,
    "number": 11,
    "key": "55:11",
    "textAr": "فِيهَا فَـٰكِهَةٌ وَٱلنَّخْلُ ذَاتُ ٱلْأَكْمَامِ",
    "textEn": "Therein is fruit and palm trees having sheaths [of dates]",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4913,
    "number": 12,
    "key": "55:12",
    "textAr": "وَٱلْحَبُّ ذُو ٱلْعَصْفِ وَٱلرَّيْحَانُ",
    "textEn": "And grain having husks and scented plants.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4914,
    "number": 13,
    "key": "55:13",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4915,
    "number": 14,
    "key": "55:14",
    "textAr": "خَلَقَ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ مِن صَلْصَـٰلٍ كَٱلْفَخَّارِ",
    "textEn": "He created man from clay like [that of] pottery.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4916,
    "number": 15,
    "key": "55:15",
    "textAr": "وَخَلَقَ ٱلْجَآنَّ مِن مَّارِجٍ مِّن نَّارٍ",
    "textEn": "And He created the jinn from a smokeless flame of fire.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4917,
    "number": 16,
    "key": "55:16",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 531,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4918,
    "number": 17,
    "key": "55:17",
    "textAr": "رَبُّ ٱلْمَشْرِقَيْنِ وَرَبُّ ٱلْمَغْرِبَيْنِ",
    "textEn": "[He is] Lord of the two sunrises and Lord of the two sunsets.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4919,
    "number": 18,
    "key": "55:18",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4920,
    "number": 19,
    "key": "55:19",
    "textAr": "مَرَجَ ٱلْبَحْرَيْنِ يَلْتَقِيَانِ",
    "textEn": "He released the two seas, meeting [one another];",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4921,
    "number": 20,
    "key": "55:20",
    "textAr": "بَيْنَهُمَا بَرْزَخٌ لَّا يَبْغِيَانِ",
    "textEn": "Between them is a barrier so neither of them transgresses.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4922,
    "number": 21,
    "key": "55:21",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4923,
    "number": 22,
    "key": "55:22",
    "textAr": "يَخْرُجُ مِنْهُمَا ٱللُّؤْلُؤُ وَٱلْمَرْجَانُ",
    "textEn": "From both of them emerge pearl and coral.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4924,
    "number": 23,
    "key": "55:23",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4925,
    "number": 24,
    "key": "55:24",
    "textAr": "وَلَهُ ٱلْجَوَارِ ٱلْمُنشَـَٔاتُ فِى ٱلْبَحْرِ كَٱلْأَعْلَـٰمِ",
    "textEn": "And to Him belong the ships [with sails] elevated in the sea like mountains.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4926,
    "number": 25,
    "key": "55:25",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4927,
    "number": 26,
    "key": "55:26",
    "textAr": "كُلُّ مَنْ عَلَيْهَا فَانٍ",
    "textEn": "Everyone upon it [i.e., the earth] will perish,",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4928,
    "number": 27,
    "key": "55:27",
    "textAr": "وَيَبْقَىٰ وَجْهُ رَبِّكَ ذُو ٱلْجَلَـٰلِ وَٱلْإِكْرَامِ",
    "textEn": "And there will remain the Face of your Lord, Owner of Majesty and Honor.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4929,
    "number": 28,
    "key": "55:28",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4930,
    "number": 29,
    "key": "55:29",
    "textAr": "يَسْـَٔلُهُۥ مَن فِى ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۚ كُلَّ يَوْمٍ هُوَ فِى شَأْنٍ",
    "textEn": "Whoever is within the heavens and earth asks Him; every day He is in [i.e., bringing about] a matter.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4931,
    "number": 30,
    "key": "55:30",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4932,
    "number": 31,
    "key": "55:31",
    "textAr": "سَنَفْرُغُ لَكُمْ أَيُّهَ ٱلثَّقَلَانِ",
    "textEn": "We will attend to you, O prominent beings.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4933,
    "number": 32,
    "key": "55:32",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4934,
    "number": 33,
    "key": "55:33",
    "textAr": "يَـٰمَعْشَرَ ٱلْجِنِّ وَٱلْإِنسِ إِنِ ٱسْتَطَعْتُمْ أَن تَنفُذُوا۟ مِنْ أَقْطَارِ ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ فَٱنفُذُوا۟ ۚ لَا تَنفُذُونَ إِلَّا بِسُلْطَـٰنٍ",
    "textEn": "O company of jinn and mankind, if you are able to pass beyond the regions of the heavens and the earth, then pass. You will not pass except by authority [from Allāh].",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4935,
    "number": 34,
    "key": "55:34",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4936,
    "number": 35,
    "key": "55:35",
    "textAr": "يُرْسَلُ عَلَيْكُمَا شُوَاظٌ مِّن نَّارٍ وَنُحَاسٌ فَلَا تَنتَصِرَانِ",
    "textEn": "There will be sent upon you a flame of fire and smoke, and you will not defend yourselves.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4937,
    "number": 36,
    "key": "55:36",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4938,
    "number": 37,
    "key": "55:37",
    "textAr": "فَإِذَا ٱنشَقَّتِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ فَكَانَتْ وَرْدَةً كَٱلدِّهَانِ",
    "textEn": "And when the heaven is split open and becomes rose-colored like oil -",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4939,
    "number": 38,
    "key": "55:38",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny? -",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4940,
    "number": 39,
    "key": "55:39",
    "textAr": "فَيَوْمَئِذٍ لَّا يُسْـَٔلُ عَن ذَنۢبِهِۦٓ إِنسٌ وَلَا جَآنٌّ",
    "textEn": "Then on that Day none will be asked about his sin among men or jinn.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4941,
    "number": 40,
    "key": "55:40",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 532,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4942,
    "number": 41,
    "key": "55:41",
    "textAr": "يُعْرَفُ ٱلْمُجْرِمُونَ بِسِيمَـٰهُمْ فَيُؤْخَذُ بِٱلنَّوَٰصِى وَٱلْأَقْدَامِ",
    "textEn": "The criminals will be known by their marks, and they will be seized by the forelocks and the feet.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4943,
    "number": 42,
    "key": "55:42",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4944,
    "number": 43,
    "key": "55:43",
    "textAr": "هَـٰذِهِۦ جَهَنَّمُ ٱلَّتِى يُكَذِّبُ بِهَا ٱلْمُجْرِمُونَ",
    "textEn": "This is Hell, which the criminals deny.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4945,
    "number": 44,
    "key": "55:44",
    "textAr": "يَطُوفُونَ بَيْنَهَا وَبَيْنَ حَمِيمٍ ءَانٍ",
    "textEn": "They will circulate between it and scalding water, heated [to the utmost degree].",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4946,
    "number": 45,
    "key": "55:45",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4947,
    "number": 46,
    "key": "55:46",
    "textAr": "وَلِمَنْ خَافَ مَقَامَ رَبِّهِۦ جَنَّتَانِ",
    "textEn": "But for he who has feared the position of his Lord are two gardens -",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4948,
    "number": 47,
    "key": "55:47",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny? -",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4949,
    "number": 48,
    "key": "55:48",
    "textAr": "ذَوَاتَآ أَفْنَانٍ",
    "textEn": "Having [spreading] branches.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4950,
    "number": 49,
    "key": "55:49",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4951,
    "number": 50,
    "key": "55:50",
    "textAr": "فِيهِمَا عَيْنَانِ تَجْرِيَانِ",
    "textEn": "In both of them are two springs, flowing.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4952,
    "number": 51,
    "key": "55:51",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4953,
    "number": 52,
    "key": "55:52",
    "textAr": "فِيهِمَا مِن كُلِّ فَـٰكِهَةٍ زَوْجَانِ",
    "textEn": "In both of them are of every fruit, two kinds.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4954,
    "number": 53,
    "key": "55:53",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4955,
    "number": 54,
    "key": "55:54",
    "textAr": "مُتَّكِـِٔينَ عَلَىٰ فُرُشٍۭ بَطَآئِنُهَا مِنْ إِسْتَبْرَقٍ ۚ وَجَنَى ٱلْجَنَّتَيْنِ دَانٍ",
    "textEn": "[They are] reclining on beds whose linings are of silk brocade, and the fruit of the two gardens is hanging low.",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4956,
    "number": 55,
    "key": "55:55",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكُمَا تُكَذِّبَانِ",
    "textEn": "So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?",
    "juz": 27,
    "page": 533,
    "hizb": 54
  },
  {
    "id": 4957,
    "number": 56,
    "key": "55:56",
